data.description: You don't want to miss this adorable 3 bedroom 2 bath home! This barely used home has a large open kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Living room is open to dining area and kitchen.  The 2 car garage gives plenty of room for parking and storage.  A large fenced in backyard allows lots of room for your children and pets to play. The home also comes with a professionally installed ADT security system(monitoring not included).  This home is conveniently located 10 minutes from back gate of Camp Lejeune, 17 minutes from downtown Swansboro and 25 minutes to beautiful Emerald Isle beaches.  Access to dining, shopping, entertainment and several beaches is easy and convenient.  Seller is offeringa 2-10 home warranty already in place for 2.5 years that covers all major appliances, flooring and structural damage.  Make your appointment today!
